{
  "texts": [
    "At the same time, some ethical principles in digital cloning may also apply to HDT.",
    "HDT continues to raise social regulation issues contrary to human ethics and dignity, as embodied in the United Nations Declaration on Human Cloning [94].",
    "It is notifiable that digital cloning challenges human ethics and social regulation.",
    "The European Patent Convention under Article 53(a) denies to grant a patent to inventions that breach public order or morality.",
    "The European Court of Justice has confirmed the need to protect human dignity and integrity, which it deems as fundamental rights [108]."
  ]
}